'''libev'''是一个全功能和高性能的事件循环库，libev 参考并模仿了[[libevent|libevent]]和[[perl|perl]]模块Event<ref>{{Cite web|title=libev 的 README|url=http://cvs.schmorp.de/libev/README|accessdate=2020-02-25|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101225723/http://cvs.schmorp.de/libev/README|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它用于GNU虚拟专用以太网<ref>{{Cite web|title=gvpe|url=http://software.schmorp.de/pkg/gvpe.html|accessdate=2020-02-24|work=software.schmorp.de|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202023812/http://software.schmorp.de/pkg/gvpe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、rxvt-unicode<ref>{{Cite web|title=rxvt-unicode|url=http://software.schmorp.de/pkg/rxvt-unicode.html|accessdate=2020-02-24|work=software.schmorp.de|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023529/http://software.schmorp.de/pkg/rxvt-unicode.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、auditd<ref>{{Cite web|title=Audit|url=http://people.redhat.com/sgrubb/audit/|accessdate=2020-02-24|work=people.redhat.com|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119050824/http://people.redhat.com/sgrubb/audit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、Deliantra MORPG<ref>{{Cite web|title=Deliantra MMORPG|url=http://www.deliantra.net/|accessdate=2020-02-24|work=www.deliantra.net|archive-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228145205/http://www.deliantra.net/|dead-url=no}}</ref>服务器和客户端以及许多其他程序。[[node.js|node.js]]曾经嵌入了libev，现在更换为了[[libuv|libuv]]。

